                            <comment id="13149447" author="dvryaboy" created="Mon, 14 Nov 2011 05:32:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch is much more elegant than what I initially proposed &amp;#8211; it simply makes the default implementation of EvalFunc look at the @OutputSchema annotation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
